# Project Overview

This repository is an Astro web application with TypeScript and Tailwind CSS.

## Key Files

- [astro.config.mjs](mdc:astro.config.mjs) defines Astro and integration setup
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) contains scripts and dependencies
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) controls TypeScript compiler behavior
- [eslint.config.js](mdc:eslint.config.js) defines linting rules
- [src/styles/global.css](mdc:src/styles/global.css) contains theme tokens and global styles

## Project Structure

- `src/` application source code
- `public/` static assets served as-is
- `.astro/` local Astro build artifacts
- `dist/` production build output

